OL,3,CWatch moment three man kidnap man in
OL,4,Cbroad daylight before torturing him
OL,6,FThree men have been jailed for a
OL,7,Fcombined total of 31 years for their
OL,8,Fpart in the kidnap, torture and
OL,9,Fblackmail of a man in his 30s.
OL,11,FShaun Freeman, Delroy Chin and Micah
OL,12,FWalfall were jailed on Friday for 9
OL,13,Fyears, 11 years and 11 years and 3
OL,14,Fmonths respectively.
OL,16,FWalfall pleaded guilty to conspiracy
OL,17,Fto kidnap at an earlier court
OL,18,Fappearance having fled the country
OL,19,Ffollowing the kidnap and was
OL,20,Feventually tracked down in Spain.
