OL,3,CWatch moment three man kidnap man in
OL,4,Cbroad daylight before torturing him
OL,6,FFreeman and Chin were found guilty
OL,7,Ffollowing a trial at Manchester Crown
OL,8,FCourt in April this year. Five other
OL,9,Fman have also been convicted of taking
OL,10,Fpart previously.
OL,12,FThe kidnapping took place on Thursday
OL,13,F11 April 2019. The victim was
OL,14,Fapproached by three men, who were
OL,15,Fmisleadingly dressed as police
OL,16,Fofficers and falsely arrested him,
OL,17,Fplacing him into the back of a black
OL,18,FAudi vehicle which had false number
OL,19,Fplates.
