OL,3,CWatch moment three man kidnap man in
OL,4,Cbroad daylight before torturing him
OL,6,FThey drove the victim to a back street
OL,7,Fin Gorton where they dragged him out
OL,8,Ffrom the car, put a hood over his
OL,9,Fhead, held a gun to his head and put
OL,10,Fhim in a van which drove to a building
OL,11,Fin the area.
OL,13,FThe victim was held for 13 hours where
OL,14,Fthe group threatened him using an
OL,15,Fimitation firearm as well as brutally
OL,16,Ftorturing him, using weapons such as a
OL,17,Fblowtorch and taser, in order to scare
OL,18,Fhim into co-operating with their
OL,19,Fdemands.
