OL,3,CWatch moment three man kidnap man in
OL,4,Cbroad daylight before torturing him
OL,6,FThe group contacted members of the
OL,7,Fvictim's family and demanded a ransom
OL,8,Fwhich they eventually demanded be
OL,9,Fdelivered to an address in Birmingham.
OL,11,FThe investigation identified that in
OL,12,Fthe preceding weeks a tracker had been
OL,13,Fdeployed on the underside of the
OL,14,Fvictim's vehicle by Chin. He had been
OL,15,Flured to the Parrswood Centre by
OL,16,FFreeman to eat at Nando's.
OL,18,FChin collected Walfall and Barnes from
OL,19,FBirmingham as they travelled south
OL,20,Fafter the kidnap had taken place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
