OL,6,FChin's DNA was found on a balaclava
OL,7,Frecovered from a kit bag in the rear
OL,8,Fof the black Audi which was still in
OL,9,Fthe lock up when police raided it. A
OL,10,Fset of handcuffs and another tracker
OL,11,Fwere also located within his home when
OL,12,Fit was searched.
OL,14,FDetective Sergeant Mark Evans said:
OL,15,F"This was a lengthy investigation and
OL,16,FI am pleased that today we have
OL,17,Fconcluded proceedings by locking up
OL,18,Fthe final three members involved in
OL,19,Fthis plot.
