OL,6,F"Freeman was a friend of the victim,
OL,7,Fregularly playing football with him.
OL,8,FAs well as luring the victim to the
OL,9,FParrswood Centre, he also recorded the
OL,10,Fvehicle registration of the victim in
OL,11,Fhis mobile phone, along with the names
OL,12,Fof the victim's family members.
