OL,3,CWatch moment three man kidnap man in
OL,4,Cbroad daylight before torturing him
OL,6,F"He sourced the lockup used to hold
OL,7,Fthe victim and met with the kidnap
OL,8,Fteam in the days before the actual
OL,9,Fkidnap, travelling in convoy with
OL,10,Ftheir vehicles from the lockup where
OL,11,Fthe victim would eventually be held on
OL,12,Fa visit to a pub in Alderley Edge,
OL,13,Fwhich was set up as the original drop
OL,14,Flocation for the ransom money.
OL,16,F"We hope this provides some closure
OL,17,Ffor the victim and their family and
OL,18,Fthey can finally move forward with
OL,19,Ftheir lives. I would like to thank
OL,20,Fthem for their patience and assistance
OL,21,Fwith this investigation."
